@minty.
The standard for HQ releases is using the H264 codec and the AVI file format doesn't support that, so no use in complaining about individual releases. Take 5 minutes to read wikipedia or similar reference in the future before complaining that rain is wet.

I have one advice though, use PS3 Media server on Windows to convert just about any format to something which works great with the PS3. That way you can download the files using MKV-container and still view them on the playstation.
